thread.title: ROBERT LAWSON
thread.title_full: Mark Worthington Jewellers reviewed by ROBERT LAWSON

author: ROBERT LAWSON
title: ROBERT LAWSON
text: After spending many hours looking for it found the exact watch that another Jewellers had managed to lose found the exact same Breitling that I've had for over 20 years good quality full history and all documentation came with it in the original box very good price excellent condition will never leave my wrist again after a good high street jewellers who will remain nameless lost it after I put it in to have a battery change and service, well done Mark Worthington Jewellers of Wilmslow for your help
